<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Transfer Certificate — <%= student.studentName %>
    </title>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #f4f6f9;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .print-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            background: #8B0000;
            color: white;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .print-toolbar span {
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .btn-print {
            background: #f6a623;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            border: none;
            padding: 9px 22px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-back {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 9px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        }

        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 14mm 18mm;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .page::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 6mm;
            border: 4px double #8B0000;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 9mm;
            border: 1px solid #d0a0a0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
            font-size: 72px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.04);
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .school-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 14px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #8B0000;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .school-name {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8B0000;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .school-address {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        .doc-title-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 14px 0 20px;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8B0000;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #8B0000;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .tc-number {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .tc-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 12.5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .tc-table tr td {
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .tc-table tr td:first-child {
            background: #fff8f8;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8B0000;
            width: 42%;
        }

        .tc-table tr:nth-child(even) td:last-child {
            background: #fffafa;
        }

        .conduct-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #8B0000;
            color: white;
            padding: 2px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .tc-declaration {
            background: #fff8f8;
            border: 1px solid #e0b0b0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .signatures {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 11.5px;
        }

        .sig-box {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1.5px solid #333;
            width: 130px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }

        .sig-sub {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 10px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .doc-footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #bbb;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background: white !important;
            }

            .print-toolbar {
                display: none !important;
            }

            .page {
                margin: 0 !important;
                box-shadow: none !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                print-color-adjust: exact;
            }

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="print-toolbar">
        <button class="btn-back" onclick="window.close()">← Back</button>
        <span>📋 Transfer Certificate — <%= student.studentName %></span>
        <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Print / Save as PDF</button>
    </div>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="watermark">TRANSFER<br>CERTIFICATE</div>
        <div class="school-header">
            <div class="school-name">
                <%= schoolName %>
            </div>
            <% if (schoolAddress) { %>
                <div class="school-address">
                    <%= schoolAddress %>
                </div>
                <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-title-wrap">
            <div class="doc-title">Transfer Certificate</div>
            <div class="tc-number">TC No.: <%= tcNumber %> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Date of Issue: <%= generatedDate %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <table class="tc-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Student Name</td>
                <td><strong>
                        <%= student.studentName %>
                    </strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Admission No.</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.admissionNo || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Father's Name</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.fatherName || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Mother's Name</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.motherName || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Date of Birth</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.DOB ? new Date(student.DOB).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', {day:'2-digit', month:'long',
                        year:'numeric'}) : '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Nationality</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.nationality || 'Indian' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Religion</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.religion || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Category</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.category || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Class at Time of Leaving</td>
                <td>Class <%= student.class %> — Section <%= student.section || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Initial Admission Class</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.initialClass || '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Date of Admission</td>
                <td>
                    <%= student.admissionDate ? new Date(student.admissionDate).toLocaleDateString('en-IN',
                        {day:'2-digit', month:'long', year:'numeric'}) : '—' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Last Exam Passed</td>
                <td>
                    <%= lastExamPassed %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Date of Leaving</td>
                <td>
                    <%= dateOfLeaving %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Reason for Leaving</td>
                <td>
                    <%= reasonForLeaving %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Conduct & Character</td>
                <td><span class="conduct-badge">
                        <%= conduct %>
                    </span></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="tc-declaration">
            This is to certify that the above particulars are correct as per the school records. The student
            <strong>
                <%= student.studentName %>
            </strong>, son/daughter of <strong>
                <%= student.fatherName || '—' %>
            </strong>,
            has been a bonafide student of this school. The student's conduct and character during the period of
            study was found to be <strong>
                <%= conduct %>
            </strong>.
            The student is hereby granted this Transfer Certificate for the purpose of seeking admission to another
            institution.
        </div>

        <div class="signatures">
            <div class="sig-box">
                <div class="sig-line"></div>
                <div class="sig-label">Class Teacher</div>
                <div class="sig-sub">Signature & Stamp</div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-box">
                <div class="sig-line"></div>
                <div class="sig-label">Principal</div>
                <div class="sig-sub">Signature & Official Seal</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-footer">This is a computer-generated Transfer Certificate. — <%= schoolName %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>